metadata.name: Gradito
metadata.description: I've embraced the joy of using GMitos in my daily Twitter chats and have had the pleasure of meeting amazing people through them. I just want to spread the delightful magic of these delightful tokens. Gmitos serve as a daily Good Morning reminder to maintain a positive and uplifting mood. They help set the tone for a productive and joyful day ahead. By sending and receiving GMitos, we can spread positivity and kindness to those in our online community. GMitos are just pixels and good vibes.
